Class ImplGUIController

java.lang.Object
ImplGUIController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ImplGUIController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The ImplGUIController class is a controller class that does the backend work of the application. It holds all the main Transactional capabilities of the application including Loading Entries(Load Data) Adding Entries (Create) and Delete Entries (Delete). This is the class that controls the .fxml file created earlier.
